{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"semifluid-clotty-plover","description":"## Context\nA first-class identity entity on rebar's event machinery, modeled on the `session_log` exemption pattern: gate/lifecycle/graph/Jira-sync exempt. Holds name, email, `{provider,external_id}` mappings, and public keys, keyed by an opaque rebar id.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] New `identity` ticket-type is exempt from lifecycle/gates/graph/Jira-sync (mirrors `session_log`); excluded from `ready`/`next_batch`/default `list` (test).\n- [ ] A create path mints an identity carrying name, email, mappings, keys; `show` renders them (test).\n- [ ] A git-ignored config pointer records \"which identity am I\", defaulting to a git-email match.","id":"ddbe-d025-5f8c-4f43","parent_id":"e68d-b701-4dd9-47aa","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"identity: `identity` entity + ticket-type (attributes, exemptions, creation)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783735864063327001,"uuid":"8e006c8d-d6ba-4114-8c36-2570c403cfcc"}